<blockquote>
<p><strong><a href="/alto-clef-jr-virus-alert">Alto Clef Jr.: Virus Alert</a></strong></p>
<p>Backlit by starlight,</p>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;</span>front lit by lamplight,</p>
<p>a figure descended the concrete steps</p>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;</span>pausing before the door,</p>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;</span>closing his eyes</p>
