<blockquote>
<p><strong><a href="/alto-clef-jr-fire-and-flames">Agent Pocket Ukulele Through the Fire and Flames</a></strong></p>
<p>In front of her</p>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;</span>her mounds of paperwork were infernal.</p>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;</span>Walls were draped in flame.</p>
